description: Welcome Jasmine Byrne, the woman. Almost right before our eyes the cute girl who had shot with us here in the past has matured into a beautiful, sexy, fit young woman. Yes folks, I fell in love again during this shoot. Since Jasmine has shot for other sites as a dom, I decided to try something a little different. I let her top from the bottom. In some cases she decided her position. In some she said how hard she would be flogged. In others she said when to stop or when to go. It made for a very interesting shoot. Dont worry too much though....I can only be topped just so much before I strike back. Let me know how you like this unusual way of playing.
title: Jasmine Byrne
